# BOT #343 Electric — project rules

## Stack
- Vite + vanilla JS + three.js ^0.178
- @solana/web3.js ^1
- No React. No TypeScript. No wallet adapter.

## Look — Electric Forest
- Void #0B1026, sky #1A0A3E, cyan #00F0FF, magenta #FF2EEA
- Ambient 2.0 + HemisphereLight. Bloom strength 1.2 threshold 0.35
- Per-character PointLights. HSL lightness floor 0.55

## Rules
1. Placeholder first — game playable before GLBs load
2. Never fake chain success — SIMULATED when no keypair
3. LIVE badge only when Helius socket is open
4. File ownership: world/player/camera/cinematic vs game/ui vs chain/assets
5. No globe, no moon level, no mint, no wallet connect

## Honesty language
Say: tracked and visualised a detected sandwich. Never: we stop attacks.
